<HEAD>VMI Cadets Accused Of Armored Car Heist By `Police Officers'</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: SUBS 14th graf, `McGinley said an ...' to CLARIFY that FBI did
not elaborate on how the investigation led to the arrests; INSERTS 3 grafs
